➜中国史上“最酸的情话”，居然出自两个男人嘴里
http://www.sohu.com/a/418720885_624188	11754
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/97e6ab9e20d84039b2cc3cc14eb05c3a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中秋要来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">北方人民要吃<strong>饺子</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按惯例</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时南北都会来<strong>干一架</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/400bc37ad71840a4850cd39049f1019f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先停战</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来聊个八毛钱正经的天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200916/15e3aa4d8b7b4256b2eca898e7b85e03.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
