<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">在网上干过战的人都知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>醋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可是北方朋友的命呐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尤其是<strong>山西朋友</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200916/8d52064204c04308b8021a1f1138fef1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/88fec16151bf4161b71637c882d9928e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么问题来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有醋的古代人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尤其是山西朋友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>他们吃饺子蘸什么呢？！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故事要从一颗<strong>青梅</strong>说起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远古时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有位先民坐在树下乘凉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">突然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一颗青梅从树而降</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他脑瓜浮现了一个很<strong>哲学</strong>的问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/4ebf5607429f46e89bb116cc8da08642.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/3771ada718d4486fb3b270b8201a5180.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千万别小看一个吃货的实力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们深知<strong>酸甜苦辣</strong>是美食的四门功课</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接把青梅拿回家腌了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">提取出<strong>醋酸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿来调味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古人们都好酸这一口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>曾侯乙</strong>的墓里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">专家们发现了一大堆鱼骨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼骨里还有好几颗<strong>梅核</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看来战国大厨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牢牢掌握了<strong>去鱼腥的秘诀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200916/7a7dc6a77a4c459980cebd9e6f91f8f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比<strong>TOM.曾</strong>更偏爱青梅的是<strong>商王武丁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好家伙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他直接<strong>把爱将当成梅子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200916/0da94e0739b74812a82a4df59b809e7e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
若作酒醴，尔惟红蘖;若作和羹，尔惟盐梅。尔交修予，罔予弃，予惟克迈乃训。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
——商《尚书·说命下》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">梅子供不应求</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃货们<strong>举一反N</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把<strong>蓂荚</strong>(míng jiá)、<strong>山桃</strong>、<strong>野杏</strong>都拿来腌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>神农氏</strong>还腌制了<strong>酸菜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可这终究不是<strong>液态的醋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那醋到底是哪来的呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/a0a05db331c746a3a84fa8daa079ba67.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们把目光投向了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山西人<strong>杜康</strong>的儿子<strong>黑塔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>民间有这么一个传说</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黑塔帮爸爸<strong>酿酒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">忘了开缸时间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到第廿一日酉时打开时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发现<strong>发酵</strong>过了头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酒液已经变<strong>酸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/3771ada718d4486fb3b270b8201a5180.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">缸里有一股从来没有闻过的香味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黑塔尝了一口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>酸酸甜甜</strong>特别好喝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将“廿一日”加一“酉”字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给这酸酸甜甜的液体取名为<strong>“醋”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200916/dc31a5d2e1a441159c8589a43cc19bdd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酒父无犬子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>黑塔成了醋王</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/a4a5e621a48d40d8a892fe3e14715fa2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是朕告诉你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>醋一开始不叫醋呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个传说就很明显在<strong>看字编故事</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古人都是看动作创字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你来看看这个“醋”字的<strong>鼻祖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200916/4cd09ccd6a9147dcbbae55505bcb4ef5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“醋”字被发明时，读<strong>zuò</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本义是客人以酒回敬主人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并不是黑塔YY的那个意思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而醋的本名非常文艺</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">叫<strong>醯</strong>（xī）<strong>、酢、苦酒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/e7406f5b4a654dbba70e7f190bed8270.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕必须用放大镜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好好看看这“醯”字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/57e4b6fbf99743dc8ce6d763ef5f87c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从字刨根问底</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黑塔的故事可能是<strong>假的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/a4a5e621a48d40d8a892fe3e14715fa2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">根据这个小篆字形</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酒与醋确实<strong>同源</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/fb151b7610014f6c9765001398f32fd7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目前醯最早的记载是<strong>周朝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夏商还没找到证物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">周朝专门设了一种职位——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>醯人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">负责祭祀、酒宴所需的醋醃食物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酿醋和酿酒的职位一样重要</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
醯人，奄二人，女醯二十人，奚四十人。掌共五齐七菹，凡醯酱之物，宾客亦如之。王举，则共其菹醯物六十瓮，共后及世子之酱齐菹；宾客之礼，共醯五十瓮。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-right">
——西周《周礼·天官·醯人》
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
蓂荚生于阶，其味酸，王者取以调味，后以醯醢（hǎi）代之
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
——东汉《风俗通义》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">由此看来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今家家必备的醋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在商周是<strong>王亲贵族的奢侈品</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟酿醋需要很多<strong>粮食</strong>和<strong>仪器</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有<strong>手艺好的宦官</strong>才能被选中去酿醋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百姓能吃饱就不错了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哪有多余粮食去做醋吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200916/26c271e0e9a34d44aa38a90552fc46b0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>春秋战国时期</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">民间开始开<strong>醋坊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200916/443a7e5b55ea44a7af438086a61b64f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>产量低价格高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老百姓还是吃不起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人<strong>吃梅止酸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人还<strong>拿碗乞讨醋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/52e5a56737cc4cd08412bd10a08f184c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
子曰：“孰谓微生高直？或乞醯焉，乞诸其邻而与之。”
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——春秋《论语》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/1dd765fd9ff447fe98a715017841645f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">终于到了<strong>南北朝时期</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酿醋技术大大改良</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">家里小醋坊都来活了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酿醋有多火呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>嘉峪关魏晋墓</strong>的壁画可以作证</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/c0946b3d9cad42bbbcaa2d7c82c77553.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">墓主人专门把<strong>滤醋图</strong>画墙上了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可见河西走廊人民有多爱吃醋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今日河西走廊人民酿醋方法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还跟这幅图一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这多亏了工具书<strong>《齐民要术》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记下了当时22种谷物制醋方法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主要有<strong>麦酢法、烧饼酢法、糟糠酢法、酒糟酢法</strong>等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200916/3ef2a6b6ef4c4786a44f43d0fd6b3e66.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/f92ce38dddad4a3e81101a820cb91c71.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到<strong>唐朝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百姓有粮食又有钱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃醋跟喝水似的</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
盖人家每日不可缺者，柴米油盐酱醋茶。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——南宋《梦华录》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">从那时起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醋从皇宫贵族御膳房走进百姓厨房</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也走进了<strong>小作家们的段子</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吃醋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这要从<strong>唐太宗</strong>最害怕的妇女说起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《隋唐嘉话》</strong>记载</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唐太宗看丞相<strong>房玄龄</strong>工作<strong>KPI</strong>极高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想送几个唐朝美人给他当小老婆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/2215aa77af464ba08e049c87df684ca6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">房太太一万个不愿意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">房丞相又出了名<strong>怕老婆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">居委会主任唐太宗看不过去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只好亲自出手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/2918a40c8f9446e09b60e202a7d6be5a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实际上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这不是一杯毒酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是<strong>醋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃醋就等于妒忌了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200916/505f677f2ac24adbb63b4989a431a810.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200916/443a7e5b55ea44a7af438086a61b64f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妒忌只是一个小意思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醋还有<strong>更绝美的含义</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200916/3c4340a9ba644b6d90d7b0a2add2a05c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>宰相肚里能撑船</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>他肚里装什么才能让船浪起来呢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唐人说水就可以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宋人说是醋！必须是醋！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃得越多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">越能忍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心胸越广阔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">越适合当丞相</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/3cbb6d43939b494ea2632428cfac8a25.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
吃得三斗酽醋，方做得宰相
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——宋《官箴》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200916/e440403162704eda9e07420e8a3cf3ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到了<strong>元朝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醋又成了<strong>穷酸书生</strong>的专有名词</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>《西厢记》</strong>里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唐朝<strong>裴度</strong>家里都揭不开锅了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他还顾着读书</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亲戚们觉得他读傻了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让他去做生意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">读这些<strong>“穷酸饿醋”</strong>不能发财</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">受到羞辱后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他准备自杀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却捡到了一条<strong>金带</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">物归原主后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他遇到了贵人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后当了唐朝宰相</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/136476cd1a9e4852b01230f2a5a9961a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200916/f8ed1b315e174dd7b6d6663aa81e494d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来到<strong>明清</strong>和<strong>近代</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出现了一个热搜词<strong>“醋大”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这次跟穷书生无关了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剑指<strong>傲慢的士人</strong>看不起老百姓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有仇必报</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">详见《儒林外史》《二十年目睹之怪现状》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200916/3771ada718d4486fb3b270b8201a5180.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在醋的字典里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妒忌还是占上风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《红楼梦》</strong>太火了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它又名<strong>《醋楼梦》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醋缸、醋罐子、醋坛子洒了大观园一园子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也洒了读者们一脑袋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满脑子都是醋意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人人都是<strong>醋精</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/b522e6ae71da48b69c38a7dff11474b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醋都被吃了3千多年了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按照文学和网络语言发展的尿性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">含义一定会继续变下去的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这都不重要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回到最初的原点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>中秋吃饺子到底蘸什么？！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南方人妥协了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并表示——</p>
